Control Name: PE-5 (2) ACCESS TO OUTPUT BY INDIVIDUAL IDENTITY
Control Statement: The information system: (a) Controls physical access to output from [Assignment: organization-defined output devices]; and(b) Links individual identity to receipt of the output from the device.
